articles.title: Australians to vote on name of 1st moon rover - Daijiworld.com
articles.description:
Canberra, Nov 20 (IANS): The Australian Space Agency (ASA) on Monday announced a shortlist of four names for the country's first moon rover, which were chosen from over 8,000 submissions from the general public.
